SHE DOESN’T CHASE. SHE ATTRACTS.<br>
SHE DOESN’T TAKE. SHE RECEIVES.</div><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-267_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">I can help because I've been where you are.</p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-269_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><strong>Overwhelmed, overworked, exhausted, emotional, stressed, angry, and deep in&nbsp;your hyper-masculine.</strong></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-271_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">You have big dreams for your life, but getting there feels exhausting. You're tired of&nbsp;holding it all together. You desperately want to feel relaxed, supported, and held&nbsp;with a deep sense of ease in your bones.</p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-273_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><em>The truth?</em></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-275_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><strong>You can have your dream life—but not if you keep doing things the same way (I&nbsp;tried).</strong></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-277_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">When I started incorporating masculine structure (instead of avoiding it like the&nbsp;plague), disciplined feminine energy, embodied manifestation, and the H.E.R&nbsp;Framework, things finally got easier and felt a hell of a lot lighter.</p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-279_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><em>HER YEAR</em> isn’t about adding more to your to-do list; it’s about taking things away&nbsp;and replacing them with the right actions to get you what you want, <em>and </em>make you&nbsp;feel how you <em>want </em>to feel.</p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-281_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><strong>On the other side of this year, you’ll be able to breathe again and feel peace in&nbsp;your body.</strong></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-283_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-284_"><a href="https://monica-yates-health.kit.com/cd74f7e4e3" target="_blank" data-pf-type="Button2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-285_ btn-theme">SIGN ME UP<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-286_ pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon"></i></a><a data-to-section="pf-cb45" data-offset="{&quot;all&quot;:50,&quot;laptop&quot;:50,&quot;tablet&quot;:50,&quot;mobile&quot;:50}" href="#" data-pf-type="Button2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-287_ btn-theme pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide">I'M IN<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-288_ pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon"></i></a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-d557" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-289_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-290_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-291_ .ytplayer"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-292_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:7"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-293_"><h1 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-294_ pf-heading-2-h3">WHO IS HER?</h1><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-296_ pf-heading-7-h4">Trust me, Everyone wants to be <em>HER</em></h2><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:45px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eONOlN dawdJE pf-298_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-299_ pf-text-2">Everyone around HER feeds off HER vibe... they either want to be HER or be with HER</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-301_ pf-text-2">Nothing feels too overwhelming for HER, she has everything under control</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-303_ pf-text-2">She has a GREAT sex life: and trust me that radiates off HER too</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-305_ pf-text-2">Feminine leadership comes naturally to HER in the workplace and life (but she obviously knows when to soften and let her man lead too)</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-307_ pf-text-2">From morning to nighttime routines... nothing drains HER&nbsp;</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-309_ pf-text-2">Wealth consciousness and manifestation are second nature to HER</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-311_ pf-text-2">She is kind, patient, and reasonable with HERself all while holding HERself to a high standard because she knows who she <i>truly</i> is</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-313_ pf-text-2">She prioritizes HER health &amp; wellness and leads from desire</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-315_ pf-text-2">HER mind, body, and soul are wired for success, nourishment, and fulfillment every day</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-317_ pf-text-2">She lives, moves, and creates from the <b>H.E.R Framework </b><i>(more on this later)</i></li></ul><a href="https://monica-yates-health.kit.com/cd74f7e4e3" target="_blank" data-pf-type="Button2" class="sc-emIqIH hFkfQE pf-319_ pf-button-2">WAITLIST, PLEASE!</a><a data-to-section="pf-cb45" data-offset="{&quot;all&quot;:50,&quot;laptop&quot;:50,&quot;tablet&quot;:50,&quot;mobile&quot;:50}" href="#" data-pf-type="Button2" class="sc-emIqIH hFkfQE pf-321_ pf-button-2 pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide">BECOME HER!</a></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:5"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-323_"><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-324_"><div style="padding:177.78% 0 0 0;position:relative;"><iframe
