</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-a286" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-325_ pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-326_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-327_"><h4 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-328_ pf-heading-1-h4">"I feel so empowered since doing <i>HER</i>!! Before, I was usually second guessing my self and struggled a bit to find my balance between feminine flow and masculine discipline.<br></h4><h4 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-330_ pf-heading-1-h4">This course made it all incredibly clear. I was wasting energy on trying to figure it out myself. You told us exactly what we needed to do to become <i>HER</i> and I have felt so confident with my new routines and habits that I prioritize!!! Thank you Monica!"</h4><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-332_">— Emma</div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="--overlay:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45)" data-section-id="pf-eeab" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-333_ pf-bg-lazy"><div class="sc-btwLGw cPaglz"></div><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-334_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-335_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-336_">I used to think that becoming the best version of myself&nbsp;would take me 20 years. But then it started happening&nbsp;at <i>the speed of light</i>.</h2><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-338_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3" data-animation="fadeIn"><em></em>I started getting more out of one year than most would get in five. I started thinking and acting differently. I started attracting&nbsp;<em>everything&nbsp;</em>I wanted and more.<br></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-340_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3" data-animation="fadeIn">And, listen, if you're thinking that I have something special that you don't have, <i><strong>I don't</strong>.</i><br></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-342_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3" data-animation="fadeIn">All I had was&nbsp;the desire for <i>more</i> &amp; A WILLINGNESS to show up for my dreams - no matter what.<br></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-344_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3" data-animation="fadeIn">So if you want to&nbsp;quantum leap into your best year yet -&nbsp;&nbsp;where your vision board ACTUALLY becomes your real life -&nbsp;then you're exactly where you're meant to be.<br></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-346_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3" data-animation="fadeIn"><strong><i>You're about to become the woman who gets&nbsp;everything she ever wanted.</i></strong></p><a data-to-section="pf-cb45" data-offset="{&quot;all&quot;:50,&quot;laptop&quot;:50,&quot;tablet&quot;:50,&quot;mobile&quot;:50}" href="#" data-pf-type="Button2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-348_ btn-theme pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide">LET'S&nbsp;DO&nbsp;THIS THING<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-349_ pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon"></i></a><a href="https://monica-yates-health.kit.com/cd74f7e4e3" target="_blank" data-pf-type="Button2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-350_ btn-theme">JOIN THE WAITLIST<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-351_ pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon"></i></a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-0af7" data-pf-type="GlobalSection" id="97e772d2-001a-441c-8a8d-84ed60e9fb1b" class="pf-352_" store="[object Object]">
            
            




    
