<div data-pf-editor-version="legacy" class="sc-jeyqhx jfeuyL __pf __pf_pO9wkw-p"><div data-section-id="pf-0fa9" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-97e772d2001a-4_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-5_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-6_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-7_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-9_">TESTIMONIALS</span></h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-10_ pf-r" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-11_"><div data-slider="{'slidesToShow':{'all':2,'laptop':3,'tablet':1,'mobile':1},'slidesToScroll':{'all':1,'laptop':1,'tablet':1,'mobile':1},'loop':true,'autoPlay':true,'autoPlayDelay':2000,'pauseOnHover':true,'maxHeight':true,'id':'0a90914d-75c0-4b1f-8df2-d7313ab8a059'}" class="sc-bcSJDS sc-jkTopv ezNXrm jzWddv pf-97e772d2001a-12_ glider-n-2 " style="visibility:hidden;height:570px;opacity:0" data-pf-type="Slider2"><div class="glider" style="--g-xs:10px;--g-lg:6px"><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-13_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-14_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-15_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-16_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-17_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-19_">I received SO MUCH value from HER! <strong>Time and time again, Monica's programs continue to be worth every penny</strong> — crafted with so much integrity, care, and tools to implement and actually MAKE CHANGES in your life. <br><br>I joined HER because I wanted to feel in flow, abundant, and not overrun by the day-to-day. I mean… I created this wonderful little corner in the world, so why did I feel exhausted all the time? <strong>HER taught me how to use structure and discipline to get more enjoyment out of everything I’ve built and worked so hard for!!</strong> I’m SO thankful I made the time to work ON my life and not just IN my life. Thank you, Monica ❤️<br> </span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-20_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-22_">- Amanda</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-159_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-158_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-157_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-156_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-152_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-151_">When I first started HER Year, I was moving to a new country, completely on my own, completely burnt out, and physically unhealthy from the stress of the past year. Throughout my time in HER Year, I learned to listen to my intuition more about relationships/friendships that were working or not working in my life.<strong> I got and stayed SOBER because, despite the fact that I've been trying to get sober for a decade, I never FELT the commitment to my future self deep in my core until this program.</strong><br><br>Every month, I would tune in to the HER Year modules and different things would speak to me. But knowing I had this community behind me, all trying to grow in our own ways,<strong> inspired me to continue to come back to myself when things got really hard.</strong></span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-155_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-154_">- Lauren (Part 1)</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-169_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-168_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-167_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-166_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-162_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-161_">The December HER Year event was the most expansive aspect of this program. It pushed me out of my comfort zone in the safest way and allowed me to receive the wisdom from women who I thought would be very different from me, but instead, we were so aligned. Just incredible. It made me excited to meet strangers!<br><br>At the end of 2025,<strong> I'm much more self-regulated than before, have a stronger intuition for what works for me, and feel like I have evolved into a better version of myself, ready for what's to come in 2026.</strong><br>

</span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-165_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-164_">- Lauren (Part 2)</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-179_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-178_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-177_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-176_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-172_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-171_">If you're thinking about doing this program, I want to say - you have no idea how much you can expand your capacity for the difficult things in life and how much a community of like-minded women AND Monica's leadership can pull you to a new level.<br><br><strong>The level of self-commitment I grew towards my future self was profound this year. </strong>This is the kind of program that honors the feminine side of you by giving you all the tools to structure your life just enough to be able to thrive. I<em>f you're on the fence - lean in to it.</em></span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-175_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-174_">- Lauren (Part 3)</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-189_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-188_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-187_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-186_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-182_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-181_">Before HER Year, I felt very overwhelmed by my to-do list, all the things in my mind, and would kind of just shut down off and on when the overwhelm got to be too much.<br><br>I feel like through HER Year <strong>I was able to learn and, more importantly, implement new strategies and techniques in different areas of my life</strong> that helped make me feel more on top of it, okay with relaxing and taking care of myself, realizing the importance of honoring the season I’m in, and really open my heart to myself and listening to my intuition. 



<strong>I also really loved that it was a year-long. It made it actually life-changing instead of something you cram in over two months.</strong> If you feel stuck, overwhelmed, a little hopeless, but you know you want more, then go for it! It will help you in so many ways, and likely in many ways you can’t even imagine! </span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-185_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-184_">- Karajane</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-199_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-198_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-197_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-196_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-192_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-191_"><strong>I feel like a completely different woman </strong>after just one year in HER Year. When I look back, I realise just how much has changed.



In the last year, I landed a dream job, moved to a new city, made incredible new friends, my relationship got better and better, and I’m the most aligned and the happiest I’ve ever been. I truly feel like I’m no longer pushing, and I’m actually enjoying everything I get to experience.<br><br>The work shows. <strong>My partner is always commenting</strong> on how proud he is of me for doing the work, how regulated, happy, and supportive I continue to be.<br><br>The past year has been full of the smallest shifts that continuously allow me to show up as the best version of myself, and this has reflected in every area of my life.</span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-195_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-194_">- Evie (Part 1)</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-209_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-208_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-207_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-206_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-202_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-201_"><strong>And here's what I want to tell the woman on the fence about joining...<br></strong><br>That life gets to keep getting even better. Whether you’re going through something at the moment, or life is ok and you want it to be f*cking incredible - HER Year gives you the little shifts to do that sustainably. None of it feels like work; it feels like full-on self-care and indulgence that I get to look forward to and tap into all of the time.</span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-205_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-204_">- Evie (Part 2)</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-219_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-218_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-217_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-216_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-212_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-211_">It’s changed my outlook on life, made everything so much easier to execute, and helped me to develop in ways that I didn’t even know I needed to. You’ll get so much more from this programme than you could ever imagine &amp; <strong>if you want to invest in one thing that will uplevel your career, mindset, relationship, and lifestyle - this is the one.</strong><br><br>I am sooo excited for what comes next. I feel like I've had years of working on myself, and after just one year in HER Year, I have a stable foundation where I know that it gets to keep getting better. I’m not sure how to articulate it, but it’s like<strong> for the first time in my life I’m not worried about slipping backwards or trying to fix the next thing or waiting for something to happen</strong> - I know that life gets to be truly magical and I get to shape it and I can’t wait to see what happens of another year in this programme!</span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-215_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-214_">- Evie (Part 3)</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-23_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-24_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-25_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-26_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-27_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-29_">It’s been almost a year since I went through the program, and I swear, <strong>a day doesn’t go by that I don’t recall some helpful nugget or lesson from HER.<br></strong><br>Monica’s methods have stuck with me and inspired me to keep still, slowly pressing forward, even on my most hopeless days when I could barely pull myself out of bed.<strong> I AM a different woman today than I was a year ago.</strong> The changes might not be as “overnight” as we’re all so used to seeing now (thanks to social media), but that’s because <strong>the lessons in HER are actually sustainable</strong> and are designed to help you, yes, in the short term, but more importantly, for the long term. They’re grounding and solid and <strong>withstand the test of time because they’re based on reality and human nature</strong>—which I believe is something we could all use a little more of.<br> </span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-30_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-32_">- Rachael (Part 1)</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-33_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-34_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-35_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-36_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-37_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-39_">When you buy HER, it’s not just for the you at the end of the program; it’s for the you a year from now. 3 years from now, 5 years from now, etc. I absolutely felt more confident, sexy, powerful, and aligned during and after the program, <strong>but when life happens, and that initial post-program high wears off, the lessons are still there.</strong> <br><br><strong>Monica has a way of speaking to a deep, core part of you that doesn’t fade.</strong> It sticks. So joining HER isn’t just about how you’ll feel and where you’ll be right after the program. It’s about how you’ll feel and where you’ll be for years to come.<br> </span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-40_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-42_">- Rachael (Part 2)</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-43_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-44_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-45_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-46_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-47_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-49_">I feel so empowered since doing HER!! Before, I was usually second-guessing myself and struggled a bit to find my balance between feminine flow and masculine discipline. This course made it all incredibly clear.<strong> I was wasting energy trying to figure it out myself.</strong> You told us exactly what we needed to do to become HER and I have felt so confident with my new routines and habits that I prioritize!!! Thank you, Monica!<br> </span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-50_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-52_">- Emma</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-53_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-54_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-55_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-56_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-57_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-59_">I absolutely loved HER! If I had to make a decision about joining again, it would be a no-brainer to join. It's a program jam-packed with so much practical information on how to become HER. <strong>Monica outdid herself with this program</strong>, and now it's up to me to implement it.<br><br>I now have <strong>so many great tools to use on a daily basis.</strong> I even used one of them to finish the last call, which I had been postponing for weeks. It got me thinking about the small things that created my HER and helped me feel like <strong>it's not some far-away dream but something I can bring with small steps into my life now.</strong><br><br>I don't need to be disappointed in myself if I don't achieve the HER I have in mind now because I'm changing, and my HER vision changes with me.<br> </span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-60_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-62_">- Audrone</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-63_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-64_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-65_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-66_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-67_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-69_">This program is like the podcast on steroids. I loved the podcast and thought I was getting so much information and takeaways (which I was), but the <strong>information and tips from HER have elevated my life exponentially.</strong> </span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-70_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-72_">- Kaleigh</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-73_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-74_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-75_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-76_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-77_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-79_">Monica's program HER offers a different spin on Monica's work. I have done multiple of Monica's programs, and <strong>she never disappoints. HER was a lot more action-focused than previous programs, and I really enjoyed that aspect.</strong> Monica does an excellent job at creating unique programs while maintaining consistency in her creativity. HER provided a blueprint for change in multiple areas of life. Thank you, Monica!! </span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-80_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-82_">- Abbie</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-83_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-84_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-85_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-86_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-87_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-89_">"As per usual, Monica delivers a jam-packed program full of amazing information, tips and tricks. I made it through a really hectic period of my life with all these tips, without getting overwhelmed, losing sleep or skipping meals. And I will keep repeating the calls to pick up new nuggets to use. Thank you so much!"  </span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-90_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-92_">- Iris</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-93_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-94_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-95_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-96_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-97_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-99_">"It is like I found the spring in my step&nbsp;I was looking for. HER made every thing I was thinking about and could nearly touch, concreet and attainable.&nbsp;Now I can and will lean on this&nbsp;program&nbsp;to go far ahead in my life. I am so thankful. </span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-100_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-102_">- Floriane</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-103_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-104_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-105_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-106_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-107_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-109_">“Monica, I would say that you have changed my life but it goes so much deeper than that. You have transformed my life. You have made me a better woman, a better partner, a better lover, a better friend, a better leader and mentor and I know what we did will also make be a better mom.&nbsp;I am going to try not to cry as I write this, but you have truly given me a life beyond anything I can ever imagined. And I know I had to show up and do the work, but it was your ability to hold space, make me feel safe and to also call me out when I needed it that got me here. And I will truly take everything from our time together for the rest of my life."</span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-110_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-112_">- Liv</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-97e772d2001a-113_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-97e772d2001a-114_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-97e772d2001a-115_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cgjCoP dOTEZX pf-97e772d2001a-116_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-97e772d2001a-117_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-119_">"Monica is an absolute powerhouse and the best in the biz. I have worked with her for a while now and can honestly attribute so much of my personal and business growth to her and the work she has helped to guide me through. I would highly recommend her to anyone wanting to up level, work through their shit and become a better/happier version of themselves. She truly inspires me and I get so much out of working with her and I know that others will too!"</span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-97e772d2001a-120_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-97e772d2001a-122_">- Alisha</span></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQ