oup where you can show up at their house in your favourite tracksuit and simply be <i>YOU</i>. They genuinely CELEBRATE you and have zero jealously towards you (that's the vibe inside HER YEAR). You long to be surrounded by expanders and women who show you that <i>anything</i> is possible.</span></li></ul></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-371_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-gFmZvT iwxMkV pf-372_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dISoPS iYNNtr pf-373_ pf-text-1"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-375_">You know that energy and mindset upgrades around money would <span style="font-style: italic;">drastically</span> improve your bank account. Sometimes you're good with your journalling and manifesting, but other times it just feels like another thing on the list - and frankly, you're kinda bored. You want to feel <span style="font-style: italic;">EASE</span> when it comes to attracting more money, and actually being able to HOLD it<span style="font-style: italic;"> (hello magnetism!!)</span>.&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dISoPS iYNNtr pf-376_ pf-text-1"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-378_">You want to make 2026 the year of becoming <span style="font-style: italic;">HER!</span> You are ready to reignite the passion and zest in your life, to invest in your growth and expansion, and to truly become the most magnetic and radiant woman at the end of the year.&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dISoPS iYNNtr pf-379_ pf-text-1"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-381_">You're deeply craving a new level of success in your life. Whether that's career, personal, health, or relationship-focused. You know that you're made for MORE and you're not waiting around another year crossing your fingers. <span style="font-style: italic;">You're doing something about it.&nbsp;</span></span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-382_ pf-bg-lazy pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-383_"><a href="https://monicayates.myflodesk.com/dez4olktgj" target="_blank" data-pf-type="Button" class="sc-cwHqhk iHTtwH pf-384_ pf-button-1 btn-theme px-1 pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-386_">Waitlist, Please!</span></a><a data-to-section="pf-e641" data-offset="{&quot;all&quot;:50,&quot;laptop&quot;:50,&quot;tablet&quot;:50,&quot;mobile&quot;:50}" href="#" data-pf-type="Button" class="sc-cwHqhk iHTtwH pf-387_ pf-button-1 btn-theme px-1 pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-389_">YES YES YES,&nbsp;I'm in!!</span></a><a data-pf-type="Button" class="sc-cwHqhk iHTtwH pf-390_ pf-button-1 btn-theme px-1 pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-392_">YES YES YES,&nbsp;I'm in!!</span></a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-7eb9" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-393_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-394_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-395_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-396_ pf-heading-1-h3">This is a holistic experience where creating your dream life isn't just about high
