on&nbsp;to be strong, your manifestations to be  fruitful, and your self-respect to be unwaveringly embodied.<br></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-555_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The creation of your dream life, dream relationship, and dream self… doesn’t just happen because you’re lucky.&nbsp;<strong>It  happens because you choose to make that your reality day after day after day.</strong><br></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-557_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">You take action because you know that aligned action&nbsp;always reaps rewards.&nbsp;It’s definitely not&nbsp;easy creating the life of your dreams - but it’s always&nbsp;worth it.&nbsp;<br></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-559_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">So, I challenge you&nbsp;to make a decision that your future self would’ve already made to get you to the place where  she already is. <span style="font-style: italic;">You ready?</span></p><a href="https://monica-yates-health.kit.com/cd74f7e4e3" target="_blank" data-pf-type="Button2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-561_ btn-theme">JOIN THE WAITLIST<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-562_ pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon"></i></a><a data-to-section="pf-cb45" data-offset="{&quot;all&quot;:50,&quot;laptop&quot;:50,&quot;tablet&quot;:50,&quot;mobile&quot;:50}" href="#" data-pf-type="Button2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-563_ btn-theme pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide">I'M IN!<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-564_ pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon"></i></a></div></div></div><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-565_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:7;--c-lg:7"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-566_"><h4 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-567_ pf-heading-1-h3">You might be thinking, "yeah there's no way this is real"</h4><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-569_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">And you're seeing those around you hustling to the top,&nbsp;burning out, and surviving on 3 espressos and 2 tequilas a day.<br></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-571_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><em>But that's a choice.</em> <strong>You have a choice to continue to live out the story you've been told... or to change it.</strong><br></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-573_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This program is purposely designed for the busy woman that wants to&nbsp;do it all&nbsp;and have it all  without having to default to her masculine.<br></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-575_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><strong>If you're feeling the urge, trust it. </strong>The universe rewards big action. Quantum leaps don't happen when you're listening  to your ego. Quantum leaps are inside the things that scare you, that "don't make sense," and that your brain says <em>"I'll do that next time."</em><br></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-577_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Your brain is wired to keep you in your comfort zone and have you playing small where it knows you're safe.<br></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-579_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">So this isn't about doing what's logical. <strong>Your wildest manifeststions do not happen from living a logical life.</strong><br></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-581_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><em>They happen when you're being illogical,</em> trusting your heart, and being guided by your intuition. And your intuition will <em>never</em> steer you in the wrong direction.<br></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-583_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">While hard work, passion, and extra hours <span style="font-style: italic;">can</span> get you to the top (if that's what you want), massive sucess doesn't require you to go against your biology and natural state as a woman.<br></p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-585_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="font-weight: bold;">You absolutely can get the life that you want and be in your feminine energy while doing it - <span style="font-style: italic;">I'm proof of that.</span></span></p><a href="https://monica-yates-health.kit.com/cd74f7e4e3" target="_blank" data-pf-type="Button2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-587_ btn-theme">JOIN THE WAITLIST<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-588_ pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon"></i></a><a data-to-section="pf-cb45" data-offset="{&quot;all&quot;:50,&quot;laptop&quot;:50,&quot;tablet&quot;:50,&quot;mobile&quot;:50}" href="#" data-pf-type="Button2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-589_ btn-theme pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide">I NEED THIS<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-590_ pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon"></i></a></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:5;--c-lg:5"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-591_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0641/6613/3991/files/DSC06453_1_ac7a2779-8a59-4a76-8f16-2f79dd2930a9_458x.jpg?v=1763751570" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0641/6613/3991/files/DSC06453_1_ac7a2779-8a59-4a76-8f16-2f79dd2930a9.jpg?v=1763751570 1536w" width="1500" height="2250" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy" alt="DSC06453 (1).jpg__PID:3893d520-8811-48de-be9e-b65e8df0d20f" data-pf-type="Image3" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-592_ pf-image-1"/></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-bc75" data-pf-type="GlobalSection" id="1f5c89fe-783a-49ab-a2ce-9f0f5cedf978" class="pf-593_" store="[object Object]">
            
            




    
