" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-625_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-626_ pf-heading-1-h3"><em>HER </em>Year is for the woman&nbsp;deciding to make her dreams a reality.&nbsp;This is not for the woman that says she wants to change, but then gives excuses instead of taking action. This is for the woman that is taking <em>radical responsibility</em> for her life and wants to up level things in every capacity.</h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-628_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-629_"><a href="https://monica-yates-health.kit.com/cd74f7e4e3" target="_blank" data-pf-type="Button2" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-630_ pf-button-1">JOIN THE WAITLIST<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-631_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon"></i></a><a data-to-section="pf-cb45" data-offset="{&quot;all&quot;:50,&quot;laptop&quot;:50,&quot;tablet&quot;:50,&quot;mobile&quot;:50}" href="#" data-pf-type="Button2" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-632_ pf-button-1 pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide">GIMME THE GOODS<br><i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-633_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon"></i></a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-7982" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-634_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-635_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:8;--c-lg:7"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-636_"><h5 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-637_ pf-heading-1-h3">WHY 12 MONTHS?</h5><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-639_ pf-heading-1-h3">For nervous system support</h3><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-641_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-23fbdeaf-b4a9-41ba-b20d-306563851b03"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">You will get the most out of our time together by having time to integrate or&nbsp;catch up on a call you missed<span style="font-weight: bold;"> without feeling like you're constantly trying to catch up</span>. It feels good to know that life can 'happen' and the program isn't disappearing in two weeks. <br></span></p><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-644_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-06952e5e-04e4-4f02-b036-7935c7b3a375"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">12 months together means that you have time to have a baby, get sick, get married, go through a busy season and not feel rushed or like you're "behind." <span style="font-weight: bold;">I've set this program up with YOU (a busy woman juggling a lot) in mind </span>- which means we're pacing ourselves because that WILL get us the best, most SUSTAINABLE results.</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-647_ pf-heading-1-h3">Long-term support creates long-term results</h3><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-649_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-bf51b565-97e9-48be-913b-bd45b3ced00d"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content "><span style="font-weight: bold;">When you have a mentor, healer or coach that actually KNOWS YOU, it means they're able to <span style="font-style: italic;">really</span> support you.</span> When you know someone through and through, you're able to feel more seen and heard by them, and can ask the right questions. <br></span></p><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-652_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-4d5e12f1-b838-4c4e-b397-5c7def54d47d"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Someone you trust is able to call you out on your bluff, remind you of past things, and push you forward. <span style="font-weight: bold;">Long-term coaching relationships allow for more growth </span>than constantly moving from person to person and never getting the depth that is required for rapid and long-term results.&nbsp;</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-655_ pf-heading-1-h3">This isn't a quick fix</h3><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-657_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-f18ce154-8a62-4509-8dce-873343940a23"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Getting the life of your dreams isn't a quick fix. We're not just looking at one area of life, or doing some basic journalling. <span style="font-weight: bold;">This program is INCREDIBLY tangible</span> which means that you need time for life to happen, seasons to shift, and human moments to come up for you to practice everything in <span style="font-style: italic;">HER</span>. <span style="font-weight: bold;">You get to learn and bring your struggle to the Q+A space so that you can <em>continue </em>to elevate your life as it happens.</span><br></span></p><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-660_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-cd448094-105b-4f45-bd86-2c70e8108c7e"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Becoming <span style="font-style: italic;">HER</span> isn't a sprint. It's a marathon. It will take you time to embody all 7 pillars to create your dream life. So let's not rush that and create even more stress (which will have the reverse effect).</span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:4;--c-lg:5"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-663_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0641/6613/3991/files/HER_Year_paddock_BW_458x.jpg?v=1763752391" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0641/6613/3991/files/HER_Year_paddock_BW.jpg?v=1763752391 1536w" width="1500" height="22