sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-715_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-716_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-717_ pf-heading-1-h3"><em>Before </em>HER Year...</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:20px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:20px;--pf-line-spacing-md:20px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:20px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-eONOlN dawdJE pf-719_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-720_ pf-text-1"><i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-721_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-check" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>You lay in bed at night, feeling f*cking exhausted and wondering, "How the hell can I get off the hamster wheel?" Or maybe you're thinking, "I wish I could get into bed and make love with my man for an hour without falling asleep."</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-722_ pf-text-1"><i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-723_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-check" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>You're struggling to get to your 'next level' despite all the journaling and meditation you've been doing, you're SO EAGER AND READY TO SEE TRANSFORMATION!!!! </li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-724_ pf-text-1"><i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-725_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-check" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>You're so reliant on your man/a man leading you that&nbsp;when you're without him (or single), you feel like a hot mess because you lack direction and structure?</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-726_ pf-text-1"><i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-727_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-check" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>You're a single woman and/or single mother who has no choice but to lead. Often, in your head, you're thinking, "must be nice" when someone (including me) is talking about being in her feminine.</li></ul></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-728_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-729_ pf-heading-1-h3"><em>After </em>HER Year...</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:20px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:20px;--pf-line-spacing-md:20px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:20px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-eONOlN dawdJE pf-731_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-732_ pf-text-1"><i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-733_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-check" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>Leading is no longer exhausting to your nervous system beacuse you have the exact tools to lead from your feminine. Now after work, you can feel relaxed whilst cooking dinner, not like you're on the verge of a meltdown (or having one)!</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-734_ pf-text-1"><i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-735_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-check" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>You finally&nbsp;have the depth, deliciousness, and polarity in your love life that you were craving! That giddy and being&nbsp;weak at the knees feeling is back and you are feeling turned on again!&nbsp;</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-736_ pf-text-1"><i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-737_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-check" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>You're killing it in&nbsp;all areas of life.&nbsp;You are able to manage your work load <em>and</em> look&nbsp;after yourself. You're eating well <em>even if </em>the work week is crazy. You no longer feel like you have to choose between two things you care most about.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-738_ pf-text-1"><i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-739_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-check" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>You are showing up as the Lover, not the Mother, even when you're stressed and overwhelmed. Being in your feminine is now your natural state of being!</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-3c38" data-pf-type="Section" id="featured-testimonial" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-740_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-741_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-742_"><h4 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-743_ pf-heading-1-h4">I received SO MUCH value from HER! Time and time again, Monica's programs continue to be worth every penny — crafted with so much integrity, care, and tools to implement and actually MAKE CHANGES in your life<br></h4><h4 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-745_ pf-heading-1-h4">I joined HER because I wanted to feel in flow, abundant, and not overrun by the day-to-day. I mean… I created this wonderful little corner in the world, so why did I feel exhausted all the time? HER taught me how to use structure and discipline to get more enjoyment out of everything I’ve built and worked so hard for!! <br></h4><h4 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-747_ pf-heading-1-h4">
