  growth-filled,
  identity-shifting chapter of my life. I’m navigating motherhood, expanding my business, and keeping deep polarity in
  my marriage—and I want you to walk beside me as I embody what it means to be HER when the circumstances aren’t
  “perfect.”
  <br>
  <br>
You'll learn my real-time practices, systems, and mindset & body shifts for staying regulated, feminine, and abundant—even when I have less time, no morning routine, and 4 hours of sleep.
Let me be your living expander. Because if I can do it, you absolutely can too.
</h4></div><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-772_"><h4 style="color:#FFF; font-weight: 400;"><b>A monthly LIVE masterclass.</b> One juicy, potent, life-upgrading masterclass each month where we dive into a deeply intentional topic designed to elevate your health, wealth, magnetism, feminine embodiment, relationships, and more.
<br>
<br>
In 2026, you’ll get a mix of brand-new topics and refreshed versions of the 2025 favorites. Because as I grow, evolve, and integrate through motherhood, business, polarity, and personal expansion… so will the depth, direction, and fire behind what I’m teaching you.
</h4></div><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-773_"><h4 style="color:#FFF; font-weight: 400;"><b>Inner Circle Chats.</b> This is your chance to ask me anything and hear my response via a private podcast twice a month. You can listen whilst on a walk or cooking dinner, making integration feel effortless. These aren’t fluffy answers. You’ll be surprised at how much one audio can unlock your next leap. Inclusive of Private Telegram channel (optional for wins, extra nuggets, and Q&As along the way.)
</h4></div><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-774_"><h4 style="color:#FFF; font-weight: 400;"><b>A full-on community of like-minded women.</b> This is seriously one of the most valuable parts of
  this program. And let me be clear, just how much this means to me—we’ve committed to making 2026 even more
  high-calibre than 2025 because we know that those around you influence you. In 2026, you will be around a village of
  driven, emotionally intelligent women who are devoted to living their fullest, richest, most nourished lives.
</h4></div><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-775_"><h4 style="color:#FFF; font-weight: 400;"><b>Community Connection Calls.</b> Every other month, HER Year gets more personal. You'll drop into smaller breakout rooms to connect with the women beside you in this journey so that you can experience the nourishment in your nervous system from having a village. In 2026, these community calls will be even more curated, high-level conversations leaving you feeling light, expanded, and deeply supported in the way you want from your inner circle.
</h4></div><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-776_"><h4 style="color:#FFF; font-weight: 400;"><b>Two In-Person Experiences.</b> Hear me when I tell you the power of being
  in person with other expansive, like-minded women. Nothing uplevels you, accelerates you, and energises you like being
  in a room with women who get it.
  <br>
  <br>
In 2026, we're turning it up. April will be at my home in Atlanta, with a black-tie cocktail night following (your date included).* December will be in London for our holiday-themed event that will end your year in wealth, warmth, and nourishing sisterhood.
</h4>
