olumn" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-878_"><h5 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-879_ pf-heading-1-h3">PARIS AND ITALY OBSESSED, PILATES LOVER, MUM TO 4 DOGS &amp; A LITTLE MAN, AND PASSIONATE AS HELL ABOUT MY WORK</h5><h4 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-881_ pf-heading-1-h3">Hi, I'm Monica. Your coach, healer, teacher, and guide.</h4><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-883_">This 12-month, mastermind-style experience, <i>HER YEAR,</i> is based on 9 years of running my own business (7.5 of which
brought money in the door)—seeing through the ups and downs of hustling, finding myself, healing my wounds, and finally
embracing full feminine leadership in 2019.</div><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-884_">After five and a half years of fully being HER, it’s time for me to pass on the wisdom that’s too good to keep to myself.</div><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-885_">This program isn’t fluffy, feminine teachings. This is a tangible, action-oriented program that's based on embodiment and integrating becoming HER into your REAL LIFE. This program assumes that you know the difference between feminine/masculine (if not, binge-listen to my podcast) and you’re currently working hard to let go of your masculine armor (or you already have). <br><br>

If you’ve done any of my other programs, HER will complement them beautifully and set you up for even greater quantum leaps and flawless living. </div><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-886_"><i>HER YEAR</i> is an elevated program that encompasses a 12-month roadmap (my "H.E.R Framework") to feminine embodiment
and creating your dream life that’s so natural it becomes an effortless way of life.</div><a href="https://monicayates.myflodesk.com/dez4olktgj" target="_blank" data-pf-type="Button2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-887_ pf-button-1 btn-theme pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide">JOIN THE WAITLIST<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-888_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon"></i></a><a data-to-section="pf-cb45" data-offset="{&quot;all&quot;:50,&quot;laptop&quot;:50,&quot;tablet&quot;:50,&quot;mobile&quot;:50}" href="#" data-pf-type="Button2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-889_ pf-button-1 btn-theme">YES, I'M IN!<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-890_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon"></i></a></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:5;--c-md:6;--c-lg:5"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-891_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0641/6613/3991/files/Her-Year-trench_1_458x.jpg?v=1763750815" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0641/6613/3991/files/Her-Year-trench_1.jpg?v=1763750815 1536w" width="1500" height="2250" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy" alt="Her-Year-trench 1 .jpg__PID:03dc6dfe-8a9f-4c3f-bf5f-8e72c9b28ad3" data-pf-type="Image3" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-892_ pf-image-1"/></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-f273" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-893_ pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-894_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-895_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-896_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-898_">TESTIMONIALS</span></h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-899_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-900_"><div data-slider="{'slidesToShow':{'all':1,'laptop':1,'tablet':1,'mobile':1},'slidesToScroll':{'all':1,'laptop':1,'tablet':1,'mobile':1},'loop':false,'autoPlay':false,'autoPlayDelay':3000,'pauseOnHover':false,'maxHeight':false,'id':'b5e247d8-acec-4cfa-a112-f43406847a37'}" class="sc-bcSJDS sc-jkTopv ezNXrm jzWddv pf-901_ testimonial_slider glider-n-1 " style="visibility:hidden;height:307143.3125px;opacity:0" data-pf-type="Slider2"><div class="glider" style="--g-xs:0px"><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-902_ pf-bg-lazy" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-903_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-904_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-905_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-907_">This program was the perfect compliment to Queen Alchemy. After doing that program, I had to redefine my relationship with my feminine energy and self. I felt I leaned way into the feminine energy, which was amazing, but I also picked up some not-so-great habits like not having self-discipline because I "wanted to be free”. HER really allowed me to build masculine structure from a feminine place, and it feels SO different than how my masculine structure was before. Now I’m choosing to do these things for myself instead of forcing myself to do them “because I have to.” It makes all the difference in the world. </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-908_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-910_">- GabriElle</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-911_ pf-bg-lazy" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-912_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-913_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-914_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-916_">This is unlike any other program Monica has. It’s not healing in the same way; it’s about actually showing up in your life the way your ideal self would (and what that means in a practical way). The live Q+A is worth the cost alone. Monica always shows up with such sincerity and wisdom. It’s invaluable.&nbsp;I also liked having the Telegram channel for reminders throughout the program to keep me coming back to the practices in my day-to-day. Plus, the random audio messages from Monica are fire.</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-917_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-919_">- Meghan</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-920_ pf-bg-lazy" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-921_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-922_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-923_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-925_">Here's what I would say to someone on the fence about joining HER:To be honest, sometimes I wonder how I was holding my life together *before* HER. This program truly changed the way I operate on the day-to-day, not only to reach my life goals but also to feel better every single day. With HER, I have been able to experience a fuller life by really make things happen. I learned that it IS possible to improve how I want to feel at any given moment by making slight changes that make the biggest difference (changing places to work, asking your body how to relax, etc).&nbsp;&nbsp;FYI: My period came back during the program so that was gold!!</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-926_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-928_">- Marianne</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-929_ pf-bg-lazy" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-930_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-931_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-932_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-934_">Before HER, my mornings were typically stressful. Now, a win for me is that I get to move at a leisurely pace, enjoy my breakfast at the table, drive the actual speed limit to work, and show up early in a calm, joyful mood. It's changed the whole trajectory of my day! Thank you for all the helpful tips, inspiration, and motivation!</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-935_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-937_">- Margot</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-938_ pf-bg-lazy" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-939_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-940_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-941_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-943_">I joined this program because I knew how I wanted my life to look but I wasn't exactly sure what I needed to do on the DAILY to get myself there. I was looking for ACTIONS to take and man...this program delivers.If you want to overhaul your life in a way that actually feels good and also works for YOU and your daily routine – HER is super easy to digest, fun, and extremely actionable. Since completing HER, my health routine and workday have taken a complete 180. Gone are the days of just suffering with symptoms and not doing anything about it. I feel so much more curious and loving toward my body and I'm excited to be on this new, lifelong journey of loving and taking care of it.&nbsp;</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-944_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-946_">- Makenna</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-947_ pf-bg-lazy" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-948_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-949_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-950_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-952_">In my third month of HER, I was able to develop my business model and things took off fast from there. I feel like I am telling myself it's okay to slow down because everything is happening fast! I have already been offered an opportunity to bring my expertise to workshops at a very prestigious female club where I live!<br><br>I want to say I would not be here without Monica and the program of HER.<br> <br>It was her third podcast, The Money Fear of Investing in Yourself, that I listened to a year ago that changed my mindset on how I value myself. It launched a stream of inspirational thoughts and showed me the direction I wanted to go in my career. I dove deeper into Monica's work which led me to HER. Once I had the tools in place from this program, I had the space in my life for this business! I am forever grateful. I know deep down that I will be leaning into Monica's expertise SO much more.&nbsp;</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-953_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-955_">- Danielle</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-956_ pf-bg-lazy" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-957_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-958_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-959_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-961_">ANOTHER WIN: This is the program that keeps on giving! I have seen huge health improvements (better sleep, losing weight, my cycle has come back, and is even more regular than before!) since completing HER - even my mom has noticed!I've also seen success at work. My performance has been recognized by my managers and I have been complimented, and I feel overall more happiness. Thank you again!</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-962_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-964_">- Marianne</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-965_ pf-bg-lazy" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-966_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-967_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-968_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-970_">If you are on the fence about doing the program HER, this is your sign to do it now! I can't express enough how transformative the HER program has been for me. It's unlike any personal growth journey I've ever experienced. The work I did in HER opened a door to a whole new world for me. In just the first two months, I was able to implement changes that led to massive upgrades in my health, self-care, and self-love. <br>I found balance in my responsibilities, and suddenly, everything became more attainable. Friends I’ve known for years have commented on how amazing I look, and my husband constantly tells me that I’m the hottest I’ve ever been. Our relationship has reached new heights—it's healthy, has polarity, and is incredibly spicy. <br>Monica's insights on nervous system expansion have made me a better partner and parent. By the last month of HER, I gained the confidence I needed and I had the room in my life to start my own business, which has taken off faster than I ever imagined. I truly owe this incredible transformation to Monica; it would not have been possible without HER. This program has been an epic life upgrade in countless ways.&nbsp;</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-971_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-973_">- DaniellE</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><button type="button" aria-label="Previous" class="glider-prev glider-nav glider-nav-1"></button><button type="button" aria-label="Next" class="glider-next glider-nav glider-nav-1"></button></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-0933" data-pf-type="GlobalSection" id="134df04f-d9b9-4330-9b86-1ea37384ae52" class="pf-974_" store="[object Object]">
            
            




    
